    <text>These are the attributes required for the graphical representation of the yard, and its
contents. A Terminal has one, as do the terminalAreas depicted upon it.
All of the stuff in here is used to represent what the area will look like in CM_WindowByNameDict,
height etc are all pixel measurements supplied from custom controls etc..</text>
